{"tid":763252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國男搭高鐵大聲狂講電話 讓英國節目主持人快瘋了","createTime":"2018-08-01T03:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T12:21:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":100,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5c7e83894297933eab91e5240c5655ada33968","tid":763252,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/112016_a9c883cc6e03af9f56a4e513c7cd5e65.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F112016_a9c883cc6e03af9f56a4e513c7cd5e65.png&h=201818bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期內網路瘋傳1段影片，英國知名汽車節目《Top Gear》主持人傑瑞米&middot;克拉克森（Jeremy Clarkson）本月27日乘坐中國高鐵，不料後方中國乘客大聲講手機且持續數小時，讓他不禁錄影並在片中狂呼「閉嘴」。<br />\n<br />\n傑瑞米&middot;克拉克森將影片上傳至個人Instagram帳號，從中可見1名中國籍男子飛快地對著手機喃喃自語，且語句相當清晰，足見音量真的很大，傑瑞米對此感到相當困擾，很小聲的對著鏡頭說了4次閉嘴，連旁邊友人見狀都笑了出來，但該名中國籍男子依舊沒有察覺。<br />\n<br />\n傑瑞米在貼文中描述該名中國男子講電話「已經持續了好幾個小時」，許多中國網友對此痛批他的「不文明行為」，紛紛對此致上歉意，但也有人認為傑瑞米大可直接將男子的音量調小，其他中國網友則認為「太丟人了」、「這種人其實很討厭，但是沒辦法」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，傑瑞米與節目團隊上個月抵達香港，就此在中國各地取景，為下一季的電視節目做準備，並常常在個人Instagram帳號發布近況短文，或是拍攝短片與粉絲互動，28日PO文表示已返回英國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OW3YSnwqULY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOW3YSnwqULY&d=9oqrGnmD7sAhEau5ITWa%2FzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=aa746cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OW3YSnwqULY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2504967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2504967&d=9oqrGnmD7sAhEau5ITWa%2FzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=cc5b2e82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2504967&h=ba3b739b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2504967</a>"},{"pid":"d266cdf8fd45406d325be0bbbebfa7913f98d837","tid":763252,"uid":60299,"like":287,"dislike":2,"score":285,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e88e5bc3936ce5869c3f397720777a3318daa23e","tid":763252,"uid":66943,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"廢老 大聲屌佢呀嘛\\"},{"pid":"feaedff03ff0ff412cecf0645ab3f8333b7dd2c5","tid":763252,"uid":130901,"like":68,"dislike":4,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"中國網友痛批 不文明<br />\n<br />\n大陸文化黎喎，我唔信"},{"pid":"34cd2f60d4b99be0fd0b3279de139fd319f73803","tid":763252,"uid":52215,"like":144,"dislike":6,"score":138,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"鬼佬係香港坐地鐵咪又係大聲笑大聲講"},{"pid":"a4d1d60c0d5bc5f325c4ddd48a9a000c3d937377","tid":763252,"uid":69213,"like":6,"dislike":31,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7d4a284a95d0a744211b997246ba4c84239b19a","tid":763252,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"即刻落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b50dec1610013b97cf71f1d951d7810e45e75b9","tid":763252,"uid":28279,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢物，唔敢當面叫人停，要上網發洩"},{"pid":"95c0a1cc1b128dd3378950148c91f20d515c52e2","tid":763252,"uid":39464,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"quote":{"pid":"d266cdf8fd45406d325be0bbbebfa7913f98d837","tid":763252,"uid":60299,"like":287,"dislike":2,"score":285,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/RSHziqJWYcM/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FRSHziqJWYcM%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=e8690ac0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed9d09fae5248b09693491f4b9702b48c5b3fb3a","tid":763252,"uid":54390,"